Package: icdhelper
Title: Simple 'ICD-10' Code Descriptions
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Nisha", "Sheshashayee", email = "sheshana@mail.uc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Looks up 'ICD-10' descriptions from Excel. Works on vectors, columns, and association rule (apriori) outputs that need 'ICD-10' description columns. Designed to simplify working with healthcare datasets.
